-- MOVES-Brendan McCafferty to be Flood Re CEO
-- 
-- Wed Jul 16, 2014 10:35AM EDT
-- None



July 16 (Reuters) - The Association of British Insurers (ABI) said Brendan McCafferty was appointed chief executive of Flood Re, the UK government-backed flood insurance scheme.

McCafferty is currently commercial director at Paymentshield, a provider of mortgage-related general insurance products. He will begin his new role in the fourth quarter beginning October this year, ABI said.